I'm just establishing the present situation.

138
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:03,119
我不能回哥伦比亚
I cannot go back to Colombia.

139
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:06,140
我们慈善机构有个宿舍 你可以待段时间
Our charity has a hostel where you can stay for a short time.

140
