She just said, "I don't like marmalade."

156
00:14:39,429 --> 00:14:41,199
她喜欢果酱吗
Does she like marmalade?

157
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:43,035
我觉得她喜欢
Well, I thought she did.

158
00:14:43,070 --> 00:14:44,759
很奇怪
That's strange, then.

159
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,900
我想告诉你最新的情况
I wanted to update you.

160
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,699
那应该是你的案子吧
I thought this was your case now.

161
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,839
