I don't understand why you would do that.

357
00:30:01,396 --> 00:30:03,956
我想这不是主要问题
No, I think that's part of the problem.

358
00:30:05,936 --> 00:30:07,995
我才是首席探员
I am the lead investigator.

359
00:30:07,996 --> 00:30:09,915
听着
Now, listen.

360
00:30:09,916 --> 00:30:13,115
那个女人非常焦虑 担心他的丈夫...
That woman was acutely distressed, frightened for her husband...

361
00:30:13,116 --> 00:30:14,895
